name: Dextensor
description: What is $TAOS ? $TAOS a Multichain DEX Aggregator that easily connects AMM pools, regardless of their providers and smartly uncovers the best direct or multi-hop routes between any two tokens across different blockchains. It's not just about that-$TAOS is all about getting users the best swap returns. It smartly figures out liquidity provider markets and uses trade splitting features to find the best routes in the trading scene. The Taos developers created a program with AI capabilities to figure out transaction routes. This cool feature helps identify all liquidity pools, ensuring precise route planning and eliminating the risk of overdrafts. The final result is a secure and efficient transaction, where all the planned routes get careful approval.
